=== 漫畫 ===
在《{{link-en|驚世絕俗X戰警|Astonishing X-Men}}》第51期中，超級英雄{{link-en|Jean-Paul Beaubier|Northstar}}和他的伴侶{{lang|en|Kyle Jinadu}}結婚，並成為第一個在主流漫畫集中締結同性婚姻的超級英雄。<ref>{{cite news|last=Peeples|first=Jase|title=Comic Books Take a Big Leap Forward With Gay Wedding|url=http://www.advocate.com/arts-entertainment/comics-and-graphic-novels/2012/06/19/get-early-look-how-marvel-comics-depicts|accessdate=2012-07-23|newspaper=The Advocate|date=2012-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120723142620/http://www.advocate.com/arts-entertainment/comics-and-graphic-novels/2012/06/19/get-early-look-how-marvel-comics-depicts|archive-date=2012-07-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 動畫 ===
在《[[機動戰士鋼彈_鐵血孤兒|機動戰士鋼彈 鐵血孤兒]]》的世界觀中，同性婚姻全球合法。

